Basics of Python : (Dr. Prabhu)
* Python is an interpreter
* Can use normal bash commands in python console?? (not all!!)
* Stick to 2.7.x and not use 3.x for now. There are problems with installling packages
* Install ipython
* Use the command yum install python-ipython.noarch to install ipython in Fedora
* Datatype 'long' is available in Python
* Integers can be arbitrarily long
* Python is a case sensitive language

